description: Lot of experience moving full time. If something requires 2 people to lift please hire a 2nd Tasker or provide help. I'm strong & careful with people's belongings and have dollies.

Hello I am good at putting together everything imaginable. From luxury furniture pieces to IKEA wardrobes and more. I come prepared to work with my own tools. Your job will be completed professionally in a clean timely manner.
I can clean homes and offices. I can also wash dishes and do laundry. Im fully vaccinated and will be wearing a mask and gloves as well.

Whether you need someone to pick up groceries or do your holiday gift shipping. Pick up something from a store across town or to do research for an important purchase. I’m here to help with any of your shopping needs!
I have tackled many painting projects. I’m efficient and detail oriented and assure the job is complete to your satisfaction. I also do Peel and Stick Wallpaper!
I am a full time electrician. Professional quality and great attitude. I have all the experience knowledge and tools to get most jobs done at a incredibly competitive rate.
I have installed sinks, toilets, faucets, showers floor, drain pipes, PEX pipes, dug trenches for outdoor jacuzzi, and worked with cast iron piping, and Commercial buildings.
I have experience in delivering and I will deliver your items on time and in a perfect condition.
